          },
          "reviewBody": "I am delighted with my experience at Little Millenium school in Sector 69. The atmosphere is friendly, bright, and thoughtfully designed to make both children and parents feel comfortable.\nRTF 1 class teacher Ms. Sheetal has been an incredible influence on my child’s development. She brings a lot of energy, kindness, and creativity to her teaching. My child looks forward to going to school every day, eager to participate in the different activities Ms. Sheetal plans, from arts and crafts to interactive learning games.\nShe’s also great at keeping parents informed and is always open to feedback and communication.\nHighly recommended!",
