            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hello there🫶…\nI want to take a minute of yours and want to share our beautiful experience with LM pre school , sector - 69..\nInitially when we shifted to gurugram and got our son transferred from pune for my son’s nursery grade ,we were not sure for anything..but from the very 1st day my son was made  so comfortable here..they create super friendly atmosphere within the school..and till date we have gained tremendous growth in my child.The curriculum and teaching methods used by the teachers are very simple and smooth for our kids towards learning..…\nThe excellent and super humble facilitators and nanny didis are USP of the school..\nRight now my kid is in LKG grade…and he loves his class ma’am.Thank you “Sheetal maam “ for your amazing efforts..We are so grateful for all your support and everyday guidance towards these kids..Mrs. Chatterjee (The Director) of the school is lovely person we have ever met..She greeds to everyone with all her heart every-time one visits the school..\nPlease do not get confuse yourself if you’re looking for good school for your child with humble and amazing team of school teachers and ground staffs.. just go ahead with Little Millennium Pre school sector 69.",
